casebody.data:
Antonio Reynaldo WILLIAMSON, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2243 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 19, 2017 LOGUE, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for belated appeal, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied without prejudice to petitioner filing an appropriate petition in the circuit court.
